				Functional Specification
		Space Weather X-Ray flux with Active Region Numbers Display
					Nomajama Mhaga
				Last Update: 12 May 2014

Overview
=========
For the new display, the program will pull data from online resources. When a flare occurs, an X-ray plot from the GOES with Active Region numbers to see which Active region the flare has come from.

System Flow plan
================


Technical Design
================
MAtplotlib will be used to plot the x-ray which is going to be used in Python scrpt. The data will be pulled from online sources, insert it into a database. Every time a flare occurs i.e from C to X or higher level Class, an X-ray plot with Active Region annotation will be displayed. 

